episodes.title: 34 arrests in Spain during action against the ‘Black Axe’ criminal organisation
episodes.description:
The Spanish National Police (Policía Nacional), in close cooperation with the Bavarian State Criminal Police Office (Bayerisches Landeskriminalamt) and with the support of Europol, conducted an operation against the international criminal organisation ‘Black Axe’. The action resulted in 34 arrests and significant disruptions to the group's activities. 

Read more in our press release: https://www.europol.europa.eu/cms/media-press/newsroom/34-arrests-in-spain-during-action-against-%E2%80%98black-axe%E2%80%99-criminal-organisation
